description:
BetterTiktokEmbeds  

Converts tiktok.com links to tiktxk.com or vm.dstn.to links, which gives you a better embed experience and lets you play the TikTok video within the embed.

Download: https://raw.githubusercontent.com/spinfal/enmity-plugins/master/dist/BetterTiktokEmbeds.js
Source: https://github.com/spinfal/enmity-plugins/tree/master/BetterTiktokEmbeds
